OL,3,CBlack holes to be shown in action in
OL,4,Cfirst 3D movies created using AI
OL,6,FA multimillion-pound research project
OL,7,Fwill see some of the world's leading
OL,8,Fexperts use artificial intelligence to
OL,9,Fcreate the first-ever 3D movies of
OL,10,Fblack holes.
OL,12,FKazunori Akiyama is joining Heriot-
OL,13,FWatt University for the TomoGrav
OL,14,Fproject, which is being funded through
OL,15,Fa #4 million fellowship.
OL,17,FHe was previously involved in creating
OL,18,Fthe first images of black holes,
OL,19,Fstellar bodies which are so dense
OL,20,Fnothing ` including light ` can escape.
