OL,3,CBlack holes to be shown in action in
OL,4,Cfirst 3D movies created using AI
OL,6,FThe team will create 3D movies showing
OL,7,Fhow plasma flows around black holes,
OL,8,Fdemonstrating how time and space is
OL,9,Fbent by their extreme gravity.
OL,11,FIt is hoped the AI techniques being
OL,12,Fdeveloped will also speed up MRI scans
OL,13,Ffor heart and liver patients and
OL,14,Fimprove climate monitoring systems.
