OL,3,CBlack holes to be shown in action in
OL,4,Cfirst 3D movies created using AI
OL,6,FDr Akiyama, who is joining Heriot-Watt
OL,7,Ffrom the Massachusetts Institute of
OL,8,FTechnology, said: "The first images of
OL,9,Fblack holes were extraordinary steps
OL,10,Fforward, but they were only fragments
OL,11,Fof what these astronomical objects are
OL,12,Fdoing.
OL,14,F"Our collaboration brings together two
OL,15,Fexpert communities, black hole
OL,16,Fastronomy and artificial intelligence,
OL,17,Fand it is at this interface that
OL,18,Fpathbreaking progress can now be made.
