OL,3,CBlack holes to be shown in action in
OL,4,Cfirst 3D movies created using AI
OL,6,F"By combining world-leading telescope
OL,7,Fcapabilities with Heriot-Watt's
OL,8,Fstrengths in computational imaging, we
OL,9,Fwill be able to follow the dynamics
OL,10,Faround black holes in a way that has
OL,11,Fnever been possible before.
OL,13,F"Instead of a single blurred frame, we
OL,14,Fwill see how plasma moves, how
OL,15,Fmagnetic fields evolve, and how
OL,16,Fgravity shapes everything around the
OL,17,Fevent horizon.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
