OL,3,CBlack holes to be shown in action in
OL,4,Cfirst 3D movies created using AI
OL,6,F"That shift, from still images to time-
OL,7,Fresolved structure, will fundamentally
OL,8,Fchange the scientific questions we can
OL,9,Fask and change our understanding of
OL,10,Fthe universe."
OL,12,FDr Akiyama will be joined by Professor
OL,13,FYves Wiaux, who is an expert in using
OL,14,Fartificial intelligence to create
OL,15,Fimages using incomplete data.
