OL,3,CBlack holes to be shown in action in
OL,4,Cfirst 3D movies created using AI
OL,6,FHe said: "Dr Akiyama and colleagues
OL,7,Fbring world-leading expertise in the
OL,8,Ftelescopes and observations that will
OL,9,Fbring exquisite black hole data, while
OL,10,Four methods in AI and computational
OL,11,Fimaging provide the tools needed to
OL,12,Finterpret that data.
OL,14,F"Our collaboration built on
OL,15,Fcomplementary strengths positions both
OL,16,FHeriot-Watt and the UK to contribute
OL,17,Fmeaningfully to a field that is now
OL,18,Ftaking shape worldwide."
